➜老司机翻车了！文案界的“扛把”被罚81万，色情擦边不再好使
http://www.sohu.com/a/424943469_115318	54832
<p class="ql-align-center">近日，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">#杜蕾斯因内涵广告被罚81万#</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">话题上了微博热搜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>达到了惊人的10亿阅读量！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这到底是怎么一回事？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201015/5a684cda05a6412e9ac03e2b94c54346.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">众所周知</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杜蕾斯是一家被避孕套耽误的广告创意公司</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其营销案例可以说是业界的教科书了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这次居然因内涵广告被处罚？？？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>究竟是怎么回事？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201015/0ed4ef5b3ef2465eb9a3ec005c8d0366.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
